		<item>
			<title>Version 1.0.2</title>
 			<description><![CDATA[
				<style>
					ul {
						margin-left: 0px; padding-left: 20px;
					}
					li {
						padding: 2px;
					}
				</style>
 				<p>Changes in this version:</p>
 				<ul>
					<li>Added URL at bottom of window when hovering over a link.</li>
					<li>Added File → Share and Print.</li>
					<li>Improved sidebar post items to use "..." when truncating title and summary.</li>
					<li>Fixed potential hang on launch upgrading from 1.0.</li>
					<li>Fixed avatar icon flicker when searching all highlights.</li>
					<li>Fixed enabling Reading Recap when hiding read posts.</li>
				</ul>
 			]]></description>
