		<item>
			<title>Version 1.0.1</title>
 			<description><![CDATA[
				<style>
					ul {
						margin-left: 0px; padding-left: 20px;
					}
					li {
						padding: 2px;
					}
				</style>
 				<p>Changes in this version:</p>
 				<ul>
					<li>Added "Delete Highlight" when right-clicking on a highlight. This is also available from the Window menu → Highlights.</li>
					<li>Improved showing last selected post when app starts up.</li>
					<li>Fixed highlights background color in dark mode.</li>
					<li>Fixed white flicker when changing selected post in dark mode.</li>
					<li>Fixed remembering "Hide Read Posts" preference.</li>
				</ul>
 			]]></description>
